{"tid":1437534,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"811塞林木（福建話𨳒老母）共和國國慶酒會","createTime":"2019-08-09T14:23:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T18:56:14.000Z","uid":242622,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"4d4a941a4391fe1ce618f52f5fa73fd0ea3cb34f","tid":1437534,"uid":242622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T14:23:20.000Z","msg":"今日發左一個好奇怪既夢<br />\n<br />\n夢入邊見到一大班福建黎既支那人 大概將會有15架旅遊巴咁多<br />\n<br />\n分別住暫時住係 北角匯 北角海逸 喜來登, 會住3日<br />\n<br />\n雖然佢地一身輕便裝備入住 但夢入邊見到好多金屬長形物體放左係英皇道395號入邊<br />\n<br />\n響某地區同鄉會既單位入邊.<br />\n<br />\n夢入邊班大陸仔有個大台--&gt;<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190801/20741057\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190801%2F20741057&d=Zo4i0ptUI%2BsV2bg8TrofrKjoMSgg1pB26AL%2BN7DPQls%3D&h=a417b648\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190801%2F20741057&h=d4caef77\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190801/20741057</a> (好似係)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n夢入邊其中一個小頭目 --&gt; 香港晉江同鄉會有限公司 (如有雷同 實屬巧合)<br />\n                                               地址: 北角<br />\n                                               電話: 2570 7577<br />\n<br />\n點解呢班友咁猖狂?? --&gt; <img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/08/09/Ag9UP7.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F08%2F09%2FAg9UP7.jpeg&h=ec1ff439&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n因為香港好多福建人<br />\n同埋大部份福建佬都係組織入面<br />\n佢地係建制票倉 恃住有呀爺撐腰 做野係非常明目張膽<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n以係下夢遊果陣有其他夢遊朋友SEND過黎既資料<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/08/09/n0jdVb.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F08%2F09%2Fn0jdVb.jpeg&h=94cc6160&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/08/09/4duZcs.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F08%2F09%2F4duZcs.jpeg&h=99322058&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/08/09/7xWpvn.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F08%2F09%2F7xWpvn.jpeg&h=c7df671c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/08/09/o0sX1z.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F08%2F09%2Fo0sX1z.jpeg&h=9e2171c0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/08/09/zUqV41.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F08%2F09%2FzUqV41.jpeg&h=6b4fa98b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n夢入面見到班友極奇兇悍 似原始動物，不會廣東話，只懂閩南話。沒有足夠裝備既正義之士請不要上前線，而且切記不要獨自行動 呢班山蕃唔會同你客氣<br />\n<br />\nBe water my friend,佢哋打完就返福建，千萬不要硬碰，如想止戰，大家一齊起這些福建同鄉會會長的底，以戰止戰，不戰而屈人之兵，不希望有任何一個同行的人受傷流血，抗爭的路非常漫長，我們一起走下去！<br />\n<br />\n香港人，加油！"},{"pid":"b5aaf0c10d7f9a91ef03f467124524658f99224a","tid":1437534,"uid":58883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4d4a941a4391fe1ce618f52f5fa73fd0ea3cb34f","tid":1437534,"uid":242622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T14:23:20.000Z","msg":"今日發左一個好奇怪既夢<br />\n<br />\n夢入邊見到一大班福建黎既支那人 大概將會有15架旅遊巴咁多<br />\n<br />\n分別住暫時住係 北角匯 北角海逸 喜來登, 會住3日<br />\n<br />\n雖然佢地一身輕便裝備入住 但夢入邊見到好多金屬長形物體放左係英皇道395號入邊<br />\n<br />\n響某地區同鄉會既單位入邊.<br />\n<br />\n夢入邊班大陸仔有個大台--&gt;<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190801/20741057\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190801%2F20741057&d=Zo4i0ptUI%2BsV2bg8TrofrKjoMSgg1pB26AL%2BN7DPQls%3D&h=a417b648\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190801%2F20741057&h=d4caef77\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190801/20741057</a> (好似係)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n夢入邊其中一個小頭目 --&gt; 香港晉江同鄉會有限公司 (如有雷同 實屬巧合)<br />\n  